text: Parabrimus alboscutellatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936.BioLib.cz - Parabrimus alboscutellatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1936
title: Parabrimus alboscutellatus
